The evidence with the title 'What you need to know about Obama's latest student loan plan ... ' says Dec 18, 2015  ... On thursday , millions of Americans became eligible to take advantage of the government 's most generous student loan repayment plan. The repayment program , known as revised pay as you earn or repaye, caps borrowers' monthly bills to 10 percent of their income and forgives the debt after 20 years  ... 
